Qatar, 2022 Soccer World Cup Host, to Bid for 2020 Olympic Games

-- B y   D a n i e l l e   R o s s i n g h
-- 
2011-08-26T16:48:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-26/qatar-2022-soccer-world-cup-host-to-bid-for-2020-olympic-games.html
Qatar, the host of the 2022 soccer
 World Cup , said it will bid for the 2020  Olympic Games .  “Doha already has the experience of hosting many
international sporting competitions, and we are fully committed
to continuing our extensive investment in sport and sporting
infrastructure,” Sheikh Saoud Bin Abdulrahman Al-Thani
said in an e-mailed statement.  The IOC will vote on the 2020 Games in 2013.  Rome ,  Tokyo ,
 Madrid  and Istanbul,  Turkey , have so far all announced they will
bid.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Danielle Rossingh at   drossingh@bloomberg.net  